description:
ecoQuery: https://ecoquery.ecoinvent.org/3.10/cutoff/dataset/16896/documentation

This dataset was built as a weighted average of regional datasets of the same activityName.  Weights are based on production volumes.;Europe without Switzerland: production volume = 3e+09 kg/year, weight = 0.7602;US: production volume = 1e+09 kg/year, weight = 0.2281;CH: production volume = 5e+07 kg/year, weight = 0.01177

Service is starting with the receipt of unsorted waste PET

This module includes all processes of the sorting of waste PET up to the factory gate. Machinery infrastructure is excluded

no allocation involved
